SUMMARY:🍄 Hedgehog Mushroom  Dec–Apr 2027
DESCRIPTION:SEASON: Dec → Apr 2027\nPEAK:   May · Nov\n\nSpecies:    Hyd
 num repandum\nDifficulty: Easy\nHabitat:    Mixed forest under oak\, pine\
 , and fir\nRegions:    Marin · East · Peninsula · Santacruz\n\nCream to
  pale orange cap with tiny downward-pointing teeth instead of gills.\n\n
 ⚠ Lookalike: No dangerous lookalikes — only mushroom with downward-poi
 nting teeth under cap.\n\n💡 Tip: Teeth rub off on fingers — good fiel
 d ID. Mild nutty flavor.\n\n— Cedar · Northern California Foraging
CATEGORIES:MUSHROOMS
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
